<p>2.国家药监局：22种防晒剂检测方法纳入规范</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190725/b47e8ef0ae4b40328ccf17dbf60aec09.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
